import React from 'react' import {connect} from 'react-redux' import {createStructuredSelector} from 'reselect' import {selectCartItems, selectCartTotal} from '../../redux/cart/cart.selectors' import './checkout.styles.scss' const CheckoutPage = () => (
Products
